**Step 3: Update TreeModel.tsx**

`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
- `useMemo([scene, tintColor])` ensures the cloned+tinted scene only rebuilds when the source or tint changes — avoids per-frame material cloning
- Cloning materials after `scene.clone(true)` is mandatory because Three.js `clone(true)` shares material references; mutating them directly would corrupt the `useGLTF` cache for all other instances of the same species
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`
